 still bickering over whether a 2024 autopsy is needed.", "last_comment_created": 1777638007061, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 11, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "A long-promised autopsy of the Democratic Party\u2019s losses in 2024 has yet to materialize, and it\u2019s becoming a growing source of frustration for Democrats still looking for answers for why they\u2026", "large_image": "j4A4HaAN8g47232L.png", "title": "Democrats bicker over whether a 2024 autopsy is needed, more than a year later"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZf6z7GZ", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 10, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8593047, "raw_content": "I miss turning on the TV & getting all* the cable* TV channels* (without multiple subscriptions) with basic TV channel numbers that were easy to remember. I miss owning my DVD's & video games. I miss when Mac Donald's had a cool looking building, & when Pizza Hut had a cool roof top. I miss going inside a Blockbuster & being able to buy snacks & look around. I miss the old Xbox (original) days. I miss when iTunes partnered up with Pepsi, to have the yellow pop bottle caps underneath, & being able to redeem the free songs. I miss the $5 foot long at subway. I miss having more cell phone options, & the options to buy a BlackBerry phone (as a kid I always wanted a BlackBerry phone, but my mom never allowed me to get one, even after I was a teen). I miss the old Cartoon Network, & Nickelodeon line ups. I miss the old Starwars. I miss the old Halo days & I miss the old fun that comedy gave us. I miss when movie theaters were having good movies to watch. I miss when AI wasn't a big thing. I miss the old phone styles. I miss when Netflix was only $7.99 a month. I miss the old YouTube from 2005 to 2013. I miss the old wild wild west of the internet days. I miss when being a kid was fun, & being able to be imaginative. I miss the things we lost, & the things that worked. In a way, I miss not being connected to the internet all the time. Thank you for reading this. I hope you can also comments down below on the things you too, miss!", "author": "Beeboy", "created": 1777639430497, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Waco419", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Things I miss growing up!", "last_comment_created": 1777641022752, "content": "<p>I miss turning on the TV &amp; getting all* the cable* TV channels* (without multiple subscriptions) with basic TV channel numbers that were easy to remember. I miss owning my DVD's &amp; video games. I miss when Mac Donald's had a cool looking building, &amp; when Pizza Hut had a cool roof top. I miss going inside a Blockbuster &amp; being able to buy snacks &amp; look around. I miss the old Xbox (original) days. I miss when iTunes partnered up with Pepsi, to have the yellow pop bottle caps underneath, &amp; being able to redeem the free songs. I miss the $5 foot long at subway. I miss having more cell phone options, &amp; the options to buy a BlackBerry phone (as a kid I always wanted a BlackBerry phone, but my mom never allowed me to get one, even after I was a teen). I miss the old Cartoon Network, &amp; Nickelodeon line ups. I miss the old Starwars. I miss the old Halo days &amp; I miss the old fun that comedy gave us. I miss when movie theaters were having good movies to watch. I miss when AI wasn't a big thing. I miss the old phone styles. I miss when Netflix was only $7.99 a month. I miss the old YouTube from 2005 to 2013. I miss the old wild wild west of the internet days. I miss when being a kid was fun, &amp; being able to be imaginative. I miss the things we lost, &amp; the things that worked. In a way, I miss not being connected to the internet all the time. Thank you for reading this. I hope you can also comments down below on the things you too, miss!</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 10, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZf5tC3K", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 12, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8592926, "raw_content": "", "author": "OrangeManNotBad", "created": 1777635847982, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "ElectionFraud", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "archive.ph", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://archive.ph/FLG2L#selection-1197.3-1197.100", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Kim Jong Un confirms North Korean soldiers carried out suicide bombings in fight against Ukraine ", "last_comment_created": 1777641202005, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 12, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": 